Livelihood zones map of Kenya

Source: R/data.R
lhz.Rd

Livelihood zones map of Kenya

lhz

Format

A SpatialPolygonsDataFrame with 24 features:

FNID

Feature identifier

EFF_YEAR

Year

COUNTRY

Name of country

LZNUM

Livelihood zone number

LZCODE

Livelihood zone code

LZNAMEEN

Livelihood zone name - English

LZNAMEFR

Livelihood zone name - French

LZNAMESP

Livelihood zone name - Spanish

LZNAMEPT

Livelihood zone name - Portuguese

CLASS

Livelihood zone class

Source

http://fews.net/east-africa/kenya/livelihood-zone-map/march-2011

Examples

# View lhz SpatialPolygonsDataFrame
lhz
